{"tid":391011,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突然有個問題想問 有無人答香港獨立之後既香港係點?","createTime":"2017-09-07T12:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T16:21:31.000Z","uid":66240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41195317f97928b7d8a3af8303aaa92073479fe5","tid":391011,"uid":66240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:58:53.000Z","msg":"香港獨立之後，官都係果班官，有利可圖佢地亦照貪。<br />\n官商勾結會唔會一樣？<br />\n地產霸權係唔係會重係到？<br />\n結果窮富懸殊係唔係照一樣？<br />\n教育制度又會唔會一樣害人害物？<br />\n<br />\n好似唔知幾時開始，加租炒樓班友無咁多人理。<br />\n當然，你亦可以話係港共政府養左依班友出來，但點解我地好似馬照跑舞照跳，咩都硬食？<br />\n<br />\n人地泡菜都敢全公司罷工，我地差左Ｄ咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e279d2a99880732634f6673b8c02b4789a48e6","tid":391011,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:00:51.000Z","msg":"無東江水飲"},{"pid":"09beea47abdf2b7a603c6fc0d2754d6e0c9618e5","tid":391011,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:26:04.000Z","msg":"獨立後 第二日照常上班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4735a15f3210c72ba0cb87dfd1d747cf93653e","tid":391011,"uid":66240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:27:31.000Z","msg":"成個香港都好似比層霧擋住<br />\n「It's a big club, and you ain't in it.」 - George Carlin<br />\n<br />\n無媒體可信，無官員可信，甚至舉住救香港信念既港獨友歸英友都有無數陰媒論<br />\n到底重剩返Ｄ咩可以信？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e99d88937f2aab8cebcf35d5d8d96905a00d12","tid":391011,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:54:23.000Z","msg":"獨立左仲點會係果班官？"},{"pid":"15f1f02b1c8d52036dae41617ec8f7e8a919554d","tid":391011,"uid":2936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"應先成立影子政府"},{"pid":"76fd8124fb17b4f702d0d36f0f7960110745d21e","tid":391011,"uid":66240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:57:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>獨立左仲點會係果班官？</blockquote><br />\n但地產佬依然會係果班地產佬<br />\n有錢有權果班唔會因為港獨而消失<br />\n<br />\n喬治卡林依段片雖然係講美國，但套用係香港基本上無問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MSFy5yxazHU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMSFy5yxazHU&d=5wIftwkErFWQMYrS7QDuyMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=0f0af5d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MSFy5yxazHU</a>"},{"pid":"4769ea6eb3f14a1d7975a8dfde50fe41bfd643a3","tid":391011,"uid":66240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應先成立影子政府</blockquote><br />\n其實一個有能力影響政府決策既組織到底要點先出現？<br />\n泛民班友明明係反政府，佢地又差左Ｄ咩？"},{"pid":"759becdc6a26e08399fa6cdbb2803bde51dffc66","tid":391011,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:58:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24533b1598140d037e14457f5bb3ffab8ef89b97","tid":391011,"uid":66240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:21:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>獨立後 第二日照常上班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又或者唔會係咁<br />\n至少港獨成功之後政治冷感既人應該會少左<br />\n但依家咁既樣邊有可能得"}]}